Package io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.core.contracts.impl

Class SmintIoMetadataElementImpl

java.lang.Object
io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.core.contracts.impl.SmintIoMetadataElementImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ISmintIoMetadataElement
public class SmintIoMetadataElementImpl extends Object implements ISmintIoMetadataElement
POJO element of meta data used with Smint.io assets.

Each meta data element is a structured element, containing various properties. In effect it is like a JSON object with a lot of properties (getValues()), saved to the storage with the key getKey().

    • getTargetMetadataUuid

      public String getTargetMetadataUuid()
      Description copied from interface: ISmintIoMetadataElement
      Provides the ID, this meta data element uses on the sync target side.

      This value provides a 1:1 mapping from the Smint.io API key (ISmintIoMetadataElement.getKey()) to the key on the sync target side. This is the value that is used when settings meta data to BaseSyncAssets

      Specified by:
      getTargetMetadataUuid in interface ISmintIoMetadataElement
      Returns:
